column5: From the CBC ...... very alarming and nasty stuff ......  Woman's Head recovered From Credit River
It's sure nasty and scarey!!, I guess no one has called in for a missing person?. Things don't seem to be getting any better do they?. Let's hope they get who ever is behind this!!
Hope it wasnt flossed on a marshmellow ....  Sorry very bad taste but what can you do when things like this occur , laughter is the best medicine or you just go insane when you read such things ..
Lot's of activity in my hood.
